[{"title":"物理博客开张","url":"/physics-notes-blog/posts/5fd8/","content":"\n这里是记录我物理相关思考的博客\n\n公式用 MathJax 渲染：\n$$\n\\oint_S \\vec{E} \\cdot d\\vec{S} = \\frac{Q_{enc}}{\\varepsilon_0}\n$$\n\n在这个时代的潮流中，虽然手搓已经失去了效率一说，权威也被解构，那么——\n\n似乎一切的自我陶醉都是一种自作多情，但\n\n又何妨呢？\n\n心中拥有美好，荒岛也能耕种出繁花～\n\n孤芳自赏者，毋为世事倾侧。\n\n主博客请访问 [flowwalker.top](https://flowwalker.top)。\n","tags":["开篇"],"categories":["站务"]},{"title":"分类","url":"/physics-notes-blog/categories/index.html"},{"title":"关于","url":"/physics-notes-blog/about/index.html","content":"\n这里是记载我物理相关思考的博客。\n\n小县城退役物理奥赛一枚，曾经国赛Ag。小学到初中时期都喜欢数学，但受限于小县城竞赛资源，不得不面对现实中的压力——小县校物理竞赛有更稳定成就，而转战物理竞赛。\n\n当我破格强基选择数二并进入信息与计算科学专业、免修物理后，本以为回到梦开始的地方——但却发现，我已经深深地爱上了曾经的有所妥协，那种思想已经深入难以脱离。\n\n于是乎便峰回路转吧，借路信班。\n\n毕竟，似乎自己总认为的自以为的一切，亦不过是冥冥之中的命中注定。\n\n既然如此，无论所居何在，便诗意地栖息在自己所爱的这片云朵上吧，悠悠飘过理想的海洋……"},{"url":"/physics-notes-blog/index.html"},{"title":"标签","url":"/physics-notes-blog/tags/index.html"},{"title":"四处仙山","url":"/physics-notes-blog/links/index.html","content":"\n天涯即比邻。此处为笔者的其他专题仙山之地, 敬请赏玩~\n\n<div class=\"link-card-wrapper\">\n  <a href=\"https://flowwalker.github.io\" class=\"link-card\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <img class=\"link-card-avatar\" src=\"../img/main-blog-avatar.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    <div class=\"link-card-text\">\n      <span class=\"link-card-title\">flowwalker的主博客</span>\n      <span class=\"link-card-desc\">每有会意, 便欣然忘食</span>\n    </div>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://flowwalker.github.io/flowwalker-wiki/\" class=\"link-card\">\n    <img class=\"link-card-avatar\" src=\"../img/wiki-avatar.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    <div class=\"link-card-text\">\n      <span class=\"link-card-title\">flowwalker的悟道Wiki</span>\n      <span class=\"link-card-desc\">用 Obsidian + Quartz 编织的知识网络</span>\n    </div>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://flowwalker.github.io/math-notes-blog/\" class=\"link-card\">\n    <img class=\"link-card-avatar\" src=\"../img/math-avatar.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    <div class=\"link-card-text\">\n      <span class=\"link-card-title\">数术Blog</span>\n      <span class=\"link-card-desc\">隔江人在雨声中, 回首向来萧瑟...</span>\n    </div>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://flowwalker.github.io/coding-notes-blog/\" class=\"link-card\">\n    <img class=\"link-card-avatar\" src=\"../img/coding-avatar.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    <div class=\"link-card-text\">\n      <span class=\"link-card-title\">码艺Blog</span>\n      <span class=\"link-card-desc\">fingers flutter like butterflies over keys</span>\n    </div>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://flowwalker.github.io/engineering-notes-blog/\" class=\"link-card\">\n    <img class=\"link-card-avatar\" src=\"../img/engineering-avatar.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    <div class=\"link-card-text\">\n      <span class=\"link-card-title\">工巧Blog</span>\n      <span class=\"link-card-desc\">于浩歌狂热之际饮冰寒凉 </span>\n    </div>\n  </a>\n</div>\n"}]